'''Warcelin''' ({{lang-en|answer ama response}}; {{lang-ar|جواب}}) sidoo kale loo yaqaano '''Jawaab''', waa hab ka mid ah [[luuqad|xidhiidhka luuqada]] taasi oo loo isticmaalo u celinta warbixin iyo faahfaahin ku saabsan meel, qof ama shey taasi oo ka jawaabaysa [[su'aal]]. Warcelinta waxay timaadaa marka weydiin meesha soo gasho, waxaana loo isticmaala in lagu sharaxo warbixin badan oo saabsan su'aashu ka socoto.<ref>[http://www.accesstoinsight.org/canon/sutta/anguttara/an04-042.html Source for quotation] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060210012407/http://www.accesstoinsight.org/canon/sutta/anguttara/an04-042.html |date=February 10, 2006 }}</ref>
Intaasi waxaa dheer, warcelintu waxay dambeysa [[su'aal]] oo ah mida ka warbixineysa su'aasha meeshaas taala.
==Ereyga==
